					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13189214#post-4569453</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13189214/scp-5307#post-4569453</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2020 17:47:38 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Hexick</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5065702</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I loved it in draft form and I still love it now. Each portion of the article was a perfect length and didn't get dragged on for too long. The mystery behind who the &quot;unknown&quot; caller is, was secretive but gave enough information to figure out who it was. The dialogue also felt natural and didn't seem forced. Overall a great article.<br /> +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
